♪But where does the wind go,
leaving me empty-handed?♪

205
00:17:00,300 --> 00:17:03,140
♪Holding the same fervent hopes♪

206
00:17:03,220 --> 00:17:05,260
♪For nameless souls♪

207
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:07,420
♪With light in my heart,
I fear no darkness♪

208
00:17:07,700 --> 00:17:09,980
♪Restoring the purity
of mountains and rivers to the world♪

209
00:17:09,980 --> 00:17:14,700
♪Hand in hand, looking up to the dawn♪

210
00:17:14,940 --> 00:17:16,940
♪Looking far into the road ahead♪

211
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:19,390
♪Together through this passage of time,
what is there to fear?♪

212
